{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"58353a6b1d","title":"致董英斌电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0842ddb35b","index":0,"year":1935,"month":11,"day":26,"articleId":"58353a6b1d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji8.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji8":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8fabd75dd7","type":"paragraph","text":"致董英斌电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"58353a6b1d"},{"id":"3ac83e35bb","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年11月26日东北军将领量铸“九一八”大错，然而今日者固犹是食中华之菜，践中华之土。东北军之与红军，固犹属中国境内之人，何嫌何优而自相研丧！今与贵军长约：（一）东北军不打红军，红军亦不打东北军。（二）贵军或任何其他东北军部队，凡愿抗日反将者，不论过去打过红军与否，红军愿与订立条约，一同打日本打蒋介石。（三）红军优待东北军官兵，不但一律不杀，且分别任职或资请回队：负伤官兵，均照红军伤员一体医治。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"58353a6b1d"}],"page":{"id":"c918fb2a1e","publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"58353a6b1d","start":78,"end":78}}}},"__N_SSG":true}